  schema:name "Affective Looping" ;
  schema:description "A temporal structure in which repetition and cycling hold the viewer in a feeling-state rather than advancing through narrative — the cartoon gag, the algorithmic feed, the rapidly-cut influence-video montage as instances of a common form." ;
